    "By using this approach, we offer an even more conservative test of the effects and rule out any remaining artifactual explanations for the findings (e.g., within-stimuli influence from contrasting opposing ads).",
    "This study was pre-registered on AsPredicted.com (link: aspredicted.org/8ZH_T9L).",
    "In Study 3a, we focused once again on smartphone advertisements tailored to Big Five personality traits.",
    "We recruited 200 participants through Prolific Academic.",
    "Participants who failed at least one of two attention checks were excluded from the analyses (n = 8)."
